snippet.title: MASS EFFECT™: ANDROMEDA Official E3 2015 Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Visit MassEffect.com for the latest updates: http://o.ea.com/39506.

A new adventure awaits in the Mass Effect universe. With stunning visuals and a new galaxy to discover, BioWare delivers the next generation of space exploration.

Mass Effect: Andromeda - Coming Holiday 2016 to PC, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One.

“(Ghost) Riders in the Sky”
Performed by Johnny Cash
Written by Stan Jones
Published by Memory Lane Music Group and Edwin H. Morris & Company, A Division of MPL Music Publishing, Inc.
Recording courtesy of Sony Music Nashville
